{"tid":591249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航拍Formula E被控　三被告稱自娛","createTime":"2018-03-13T10:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T11:00:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64e232313c82e32df9ce637c6b5a680a26fda603","tid":591249,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180313/20329987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F20329987&d=IhKlETWeGwy2SRW03p3ARtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=bc8b2c8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F20329987&h=07385562\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180313/20329987</a><br />\n<br />\n航拍Formula E被控　三被告稱自娛<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180313/large/13ls3p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F13ls3p2.jpg&h=491c27e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告容嘉暉（左）及聶拜一（右）在庭外 「擺Post」。戴國輝攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年電動方程式賽車（Formula E）舉行期間，3男子疑因在賽道上空操作航拍機被拘控，案件昨開審，各否認一項致使飛機對人或財產造成危害罪，他們警誡下稱為自娛及觀賞才拍攝，不涉商業，不知會犯法。<br />\n<br />\n警稱有3至4部航拍機<br />\n<br />\n3名被告為攝影師聶拜一（41歲）、無業漢容嘉暉（29歲）及電腦工程師沈志青（43歲）。警員指前年10月9日龍和道一帶舉行賽事，知道賽車時速高達200公里，有警員看到3至4部航拍機在賽道上空忽高忽低，最低時與沒有上蓋的觀眾席相距3、4層樓高距離，飛得最高者達30層樓。警員尾隨航拍機，發現聶、容站在一地盤貨櫃頂操作航拍機，沈則在行人路。而負責比賽的公司營運總監李芷蕙指，公司網站、門票及會場均提醒市民不要帶航拍機，她承認當日沒收到投訴。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2666/17<br />\n■記者戴國輝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180313/large/13ls3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F13ls3p3.jpg&h=85b6277b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為另一被告沈志青。"},